%% Card payment: authorize (hold) now, capture + settle later, reconcile against the ledger
sequenceDiagram
    actor Cust as Customer
    participant M as Merchant
    participant PSP as PSP / Gateway
    participant Net as Card network
    participant Iss as Issuer
    Cust->>M: Pay (idempotency key)
    M->>PSP: Authorize
    PSP->>Net: Auth request
    Net->>Iss: Approve?
    Iss->>Net: Approved (hold funds)
    Net->>PSP: Auth OK
    PSP->>M: Authorized
    Note over M,Iss: Later - capture, then settle, reconcile against the ledger
